<concept id="id" class="- topic/topic concept/concept "><title class="- topic/title ">Payment Method</title><conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody "><p class="- topic/p ">As an organization owner or Billing Manager, you can update your billing settings, including payment method, billing information, and billing email recipients at any time.</p><p class="- topic/p ">To update payment method and billing information, follow these steps:</p><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li ">Log in to <xref format="html" href="https://testops.katalon.io/" scope="external" class="- topic/xref ">Katalon TestOps</xref>. </li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Select your <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Organization</b>. Go to <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Settings &gt; Payment Method</b>.</p><p class="- topic/p "><image href="image/k1-payment-method.png" width="400" class="- topic/image "/></p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">The <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Payment Method</b> page appears.</p><p class="- topic/p "><image href="image/k1-payment-method-page.png" width="700" class="- topic/image "/></p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Input your information and click <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Save.</b> <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "/></p></li></ol></conbody></concept>